{"tid":2214800,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識解夢","createTime":"2020-09-23T13:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T15:26:46.000Z","uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed606fbe98deb1cb6687bc297f8195c4aff352f3","tid":2214800,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"前晚發咗一個好恐怖嘅夢<br />\n就係我搬咗去一間位於河邊嘅獨立屋<br />\n自己住一間房<br />\n而間房只有一張床<br />\n睇落好舒服<br />\n但係原來一到夜晚<br />\n河邊嘅水蛭全部走曬入我間房<br />\n爬上我張床咬我對腳<br />\n但一天光佢哋就會番番入條河<br />\n而我對腳就全部都係傷痕<br />\n我好少發夢，但呢個夢真係好恐怖<br />\n趁仲有記憶問吓究竟個夢想表達啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1223ba942f7813addc5af4375fec55275aa765","tid":2214800,"uid":103063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"google<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6bab18cc6cfad1f25e9f50f2a7c9cabdbfdd02","tid":2214800,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"買屋損手爛腳<br />\n9up"},{"pid":"b516495cf115197f874f81ab956d494eb107adb0","tid":2214800,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"依排唔好出街 做危險野 <br />\n腳部會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係有錢打斷腳都唔洗憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624d0f073bf6e7f6410c9a0a9ec758ddada09321","tid":2214800,"uid":121291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"小心肩頸脊椎健康"},{"pid":"88dbe225b99eec60ee6d1b9507bdb4870de5774d","tid":2214800,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"624d0f073bf6e7f6410c9a0a9ec758ddada09321","tid":2214800,"uid":121291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"小心肩頸脊椎健康"},"c